{"tid":1939272,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU示範正確口罩戴法！只是你可能比較適合兒童尺寸哦XD","createTime":"2020-03-23T05:00:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T09:55:10.000Z","uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b12124b3291873b6cce3df98f613bed56872976d","tid":1939272,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T05:00:36.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎（COVID19）全球蔓延開來，大家出門也都紛紛戴上了口罩。 最近出街的IU也不例外。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日前，IU結束了濟州島的工作經由金浦機場返回首爾，下了飛機的她被鏡頭拍到一路都戴著白色的口罩。 IU紮著丸子頭，衣著休閒，口罩遮住了大半張臉，只露出了眼睛和額頭，雖然看不到全臉，但依舊是美麗不減。<br />\n<br />\n有意思的是IU所戴的口罩是成人款，戴在她巴掌大的臉上明顯大了很多，和工作人員的口罩下的「飽滿感」完全不同。<br />\n<br />\nIU佩戴口罩的方式可謂是教科書一般準確，完全遮住了口鼻，連下巴都兜得嚴嚴實實，除了看上去有些「空空」的之外，絕對是滿分佩戴方式。IU啊，你是不是比較適合兒童尺寸呢？臉實在太小啦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ygDbH2PcQH8&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DygDbH2PcQH8%26feature%3Demb_title&d=Eps995EZp4R4ibMzYmnfry3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=cfe72f63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ygDbH2PcQH8&amp;feature=emb_title</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/125309\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreastardaily.com%2Ftc%2Fnews%2F125309&d=Eps995EZp4R4ibMzYmnfry3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=27467936\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/125309</a>"},{"pid":"8cc22a601b263e1f454c5d4641052d0c853190d8","tid":1939272,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T05:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_516b13e2cdc601b89b5f819fc7258511/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-03-23/125309-825736.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_516b13e2cdc601b89b5f819fc7258511%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-03-23%2F125309-825736.png&h=9c245be7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_11dc6f1d543bc21b75da